The course focuses on developing reading, writing, speaking and listening skills at C1/C2 level. During the course, various texts are to be read and listened to, written and discussed. Vocabulary is developed and grammar revised.Objectives/eesmärkid:  Expanding vocabulary and developing reading, writing, listening and speaking skills at C1/C2 level; revising advanced language structures.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  After having successfully completed the course, the students: 1. will be able to use the vocabulary and grammar covered during the course in speech and writing 2. will have developed their reading, listening, writing and speaking skills at C1/C2 level.
